---

---

<header class="relative w-full h-screen flex items-end overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <img
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            src="./talking_at_dollys.jpg"
            alt="Foggy WWII-era European city at night"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 hero-gradient"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/50"></div>
    </div>

    <div
        class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-[1296px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 lg:px-16 pb-24"
    >
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
            <p
                class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-secondary mb-5 uppercase tracking-[0.3em]"
            >
                THE CONOR THORN SERIES · BOOK FOUR
            </p>
            <h1
                class="font-headline-xl text-headline-xl text-white mb-5 font-bold leading-none tracking-tight"
            >
                Glenn Dyer
            </h1>

            <p
                class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-zinc-300 mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-xl"
            >
                When an Allied mission inside occupied France goes dark, OSS
                agent Conor Thorn is sent to find out why. In a shadow war where
                every ally is suspect, trust is the most lethal weapon of all.
            </p>
            <div class="flex gap-4 flex-wrap items-center">
                <a
                    href="/books/trust-no-one"
                    class="bg-secondary text-white px-10 py-4 font-label-caps text-label-caps uppercase tracking-[0.2em] hover:bg-on-surface hover:text-background transition-colors duration-200"
                >
                    ORDER NOW
                </a>
                <a
                    href="/about"
                    class="border border-zinc-600 text-zinc-300 px-10 py-4 font-label-caps text-label-caps uppercase tracking-[0.2em] hover:border-white hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200"
                >
                    ABOUT THE AUTHOR
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>
